PropertySetDef.Name: Pset_MaterialSolid
PropertySetDef.Definition: A set of extended material properties of solid (natural) materials typically used within the context of geology and geotechnics.

PropertyDef.Name: ZnContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Zink. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: CuContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Copper. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: PbContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Lead. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: CrContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Chromium. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: HgContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Mercury. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: NiContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Nickel. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: AsContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Arsenic. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: CdContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Cadmium. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: MnContent
PropertyDef.Definition: Content of Manganese. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: OrganicMatterContent
PropertyDef.Definition: The total carbon content in soil (test method after dry combustion, the organic carbon content is calculated from this content after correcting for carbonates present in the sample). The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.

PropertyDef.Name: TS
PropertyDef.Definition: The total sulfur content. The unit must be defined in _'IfcPropertySingleValue_._Unit'_.
